thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by IAN

author: IAN
title: IAN
text:
Staff excellent ,helpful, polite .
Didn't get car ordered ,but car supplied ok.
Biggest complaint would be all the extra add on costs ,particularly excess Insurance ,Quote: was more expensive than Car Rental .
Would look more closely at other Rental Companies before going back to Redspot.
